! M-type Mira variable stars
! Ireland, Scholz, and Wood, MNRAS 418, 114-128 (2011)
! C50 5050 L  series
! M = 1.35 Msun         when reaches AGB.  start with 1.5 at ZAMS
! at phase = 0
! L = 6722 Lsun      logL = 3.8
! T = 3271           logT = 3.5
! period = 427 days
! mlt_alpha = 2.0
! age ~ 3e9 years
! see Fig 4 for history plots of logL and logTeff and R

&star_job

